summary:
What an incredible night with my best friend. I may have been sweating like crazy in this hoodie-but it was worth it. 
I’ll...
caption:
What an incredible night with my best friend. I may have been sweating like crazy in this hoodie-but it was worth it.
I’ll never get over though the fact that Andrea was right behind me-literally an arms length away and my reaction time was too slow to notice until she was walking away. I was an arms length from the mother of my favorite person on the planet and I MISSED MY CHANCE
Please, someone, tell @taylorswift I love her and tell Andrea I love her. Because I missed my chance and who knows if I’ll ever get it again.

summary: It’s so weird.. I just had to think about the first time I ever listened to Taylor Swift and none of my friends had a clue who...
body:
It’s so weird.. I just had to think about the first time I ever listened to Taylor Swift and none of my friends had a clue who she was. So it was like me and Taylor in my own small bubble.

Now the whole world knows her and it’s just so beautiful to see how she developed over the years and yet always stays so kind, loving and passionate.

She’s definitely a role model.
